name: Cosmos (Commodore Free)
overview: Cosmos was developed by Jonas Hultén & Patric Hultén in 2014 and published in Commodore Free #079. It is an unofficial port of the 1981 Century Electronics game of the same name. It even includes the arcade speech. Game description: Destroy swarms of aliens and asteroids. If there are too many enemies on the screen, use the time warp to slow all your foes down.
